* [JLS 4.2.1 Integral Types and Values](http://java.sun.com/docs/books/jls/third_edition/html/typesValues.html#4.2.1)
   * For `byte`, from `-128` to `127`, inclusive
* [JLS 5.1.2 Widening Primitive Conversion](http://java.sun.com/docs/books/jls/third_edition/html/conversions.html#5.1.2)

